      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The engine currently runs roughly and exhibits noticeable fluid leaks, while the transmission hesitates during shifts. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and wheel arches, along with several large dents and heavily faded clear coat. The interior shows its age with several tears in the upholstery, a sagging headliner, and non-functional air conditioning. This is an ideal candidate for a parts car or a dedicated mechanic's project for someone willing to invest the time and resources into a full restoration.",
