      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well cared for by its previous owners. The exterior maintains a great luster, though a close inspection will reveal some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light scuffs on the rear bumper. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is sound, with a complete service history and a smooth-running engine, making it a reliable and attractive choice for its next owner.",
