      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 987.1 Cayman S is a precision-engineered mid-engine platform powered by a 3.4L flat-six with VarioCam Plus, delivering linear torque across the rev range. The 6-speed manual transaxle offers short, tactile throws, paired with a chassis featuring Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for adjustable damping and optimized lateral load distribution. Maintenance is current, including a proactive cooling system overhaul and a clean borescope report to ensure cylinder wall integrity. The braking system utilizes four-piston aluminum monoblock calipers for consistent thermal management and pedal feel. While exhibiting minor cosmetic patina typical of a spirited driver, the mechanical synchronization and polar moment of inertia remain exceptional, providing a pure analog driving experience.",
