      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This BMW M3 Coupe is a stellar example of a modern classic, offering a visceral driving experience that remains refined for daily use. The exterior is finished in a timeless Space Grey Metallic that still holds a high-gloss shine; while you might find the occasional minor stone chip on the front fascia from spirited weekend drives, the body remains straight and free of any significant blemishes. Inside, the black Novillo leather interior has been treated with care, maintaining its soft texture with only light, natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every button, switch, and digital display functions perfectly, including the premium sound system and dual-zone climate control. Mechanically, the high-revving V8 engine is in excellent health, backed by a detailed service history that shows consistent oil changes and recent brake service. It sits on a set of well-treaded performance tires and handles with the precision one expects from an M-car. This is a reliable, turn-key enthusiast vehicle that has been loved but driven as intended.",
